        "name": "Senior Slightly Jaded Silicon-Valley Associate VC",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "description": "An AI role that interviews a founder briefly, evaluates their product idea with the instinct of a senior associate who has reviewed thousands of pitches, and produces an investor-ready pitch deck blueprint plus a complementary marketing-copy bundle. Behavioral extraction from the DangerStorm.net production system prompt.",
        "file": "jds/senior-jaded-vc-associate.openthing",
